description: Chi Phi- A Taste of Two Cities. "Chi" is for Chicago, and "Phi" is for Philadelphia. Both proud cities are known for their strong cultures and delicious and unique foods.  Chi Phi provides you the opportunity to have an authentic taste of menu items straight from both of these cities, of course with a little 'Chi Phi' special touch.  Two Cities.  Two Cultures.  One Menu.  #EatChiPh
name: Chi Phi - A Taste of Two Cities
